---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---
<PageLayout title="About">
  <h2 class="greeting">Hi, welcome to my site!</h2>

  <div class="polaroid-grid">
    <figure class="polaroid p0">
      <img src="/images/polaroids/photo1.jpg" alt="Skiing" loading="lazy" />
      <figcaption>On the slopes</figcaption>
    </figure>
    <figure class="polaroid p1">
      <img src="/images/polaroids/photo2.jpg" alt="Golf" loading="lazy" />
      <figcaption>On the course</figcaption>
    </figure>
    <figure class="polaroid p2">
      <img src="/images/polaroids/photo3.jpg" alt="F1" loading="lazy" />
      <figcaption>Race day</figcaption>
    </figure>
  </div>

  <p>
    I'm Apurva from <strong>Houston, TX</strong>. I'm a cloud engineer at
    <a href="https://aws.amazon.com">Amazon Web Services</a> working on enterprise VPC architecture,
    WAF, Route 53, and network infrastructure. I studied <strong>computer science</strong> at the
    <a href="https://umich.edu">University of Michigan</a> and before that grew up a bit all over the
    place, spending about four and a half years living in France and attending the
    <a href="https://asparis.org">American School of Paris</a> for middle school.
  </p>

  <p>
    Living abroad, learning French, and being surrounded by so many different perspectives early on
    turned me into a global affairs nerd. That carried into debate and Model UN in high school, which
    became my main thing. When COVID shut down university conferences in 2020, I co-founded
    <strong>GLOMUN</strong>, one of the first fully online Model UN conferences (250+ attendees,
    featured on Best Delegate and All American MUN). I later served as Secretary General of North
    America on <a href="https://www.munimpact.org">MUN Impact</a>'s global leadership team, focused
    on the UN Sustainable Development Goals.
  </p>

  <p>
    That SDG work is actually what led me to build <a href="/projects">AquaSDG</a> recently, an AI
    water security tool using Google's Groundsource data that I'm continuing to expand. At Michigan I
    received $15K in funding through EECS 495 with Prof. Chesney to build
    <strong>SmartDose</strong>, an IoT medication adherence platform with ESP32 hardware, React Native,
    and a DynamoDB backend (selected 1 of 10 out of 50+ proposals). These days I'm mostly
    <a href="/projects">building</a> cloud infrastructure tooling, ML models, and multi-agent systems.
    My latest project is a <a href="https://wine.apurvad.xyz">wine quality and price predictor</a>
    trained on 130K reviews.
  </p>

  <p>
    Outside of work I watch too much F1, read too much about wine, and Michigan football runs through
    my blood. Most days you'll find me skiing, golfing, or finding something new to add to
    <a href="https://beliapp.com">Beli</a>. Thanks for stopping by!
  </p>

  <div class="f1-tracks">
    <p class="track-label">Favorite circuits</p>
    <div class="track-row">
      <div class="track-item" title="Circuit de Monaco">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M50,15 L75,15 Q85,15 85,25 L85,45 Q85,55 75,55 L60,55 Q50,55 50,65 L50,75 Q50,85 40,85 L25,85 Q15,85 15,75 L15,35 Q15,25 25,25 L35,25 Q45,25 50,15Z"/>
        </svg>
        <span>Monaco</span>
      </div>
      <div class="track-item" title="Circuit of the Americas">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M20,80 L20,40 L30,20 L50,20 L60,30 L70,25 L80,30 L80,45 L65,50 L55,45 L50,50 L60,60 L75,55 L85,65 L80,80 L60,85 L40,75 L20,80Z"/>
        </svg>
        <span>COTA</span>
      </div>
      <div class="track-item" title="Autodromo Enzo e Dino Ferrari">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M25,70 L15,55 Q10,45 20,35 L40,20 Q50,15 60,20 L80,35 Q90,42 85,55 L75,65 L65,55 L55,60 L60,70 L50,80 L35,78 L25,70Z"/>
        </svg>
        <span>Imola</span>
      </div>
      <div class="track-item" title="Circuit de Spa-Francorchamps">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M30,85 L15,65 L20,40 L35,25 L50,20 L60,25 L55,40 L65,50 L80,45 L90,55 L85,70 L70,80 L55,75 L45,80 L30,85Z"/>
        </svg>
        <span>Spa</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3>Elsewhere</h3>
  <ul class="elsewhere">
    <li><a href="https://github.com/ApurvaDesai6">GitHub</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://linkedin.com/in/-desai-apurva">LinkedIn</a></li>
    <li><a href="mailto:apurvad@umich.edu">Email</a></li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Website</h3>
  <p class="credits">
    Built with <a href="https://astro.build">Astro</a>. Hosted on AWS (S3 + CloudFront).
    Source on <a href="https://github.com/ApurvaDesai6/apurva-portfolio">GitHub</a>.
    Typeset in Fraunces, Source Sans 3 &amp; Crimson Pro.
  </p>

  <div class="sticker s-michigan" title="Go Blue!">〽️</div>
  <div class="sticker s-f1" title="F1">🏎️</div>
  <div class="sticker s-aws" title="AWS">☁️</div>
  <div class="sticker s-wine" title="Wine">🍷</div>
  <div class="sticker s-ski" title="Skiing">⛷️</div>
  <div class="sticker s-golf" title="Golf">⛳</div>
  <div class="sticker s-france" title="Paris">🇫🇷</div>
  <div class="sticker s-un" title="Model UN">🌐</div>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .greeting { font-size: 1.3rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .polaroid-grid { display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
  .polaroid {
    background: white;
    padding: 6px 6px 32px;
    box-shadow: 2px 3px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
    max-width: 150px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .p0 { transform: rotate(-2.5deg); }
  .p1 { transform: rotate(1.5deg); }
  .p2 { transform: rotate(-1deg); }
  .polaroid img { width: 138px; height: 138px; object-fit: cover; display: block; }
  .polaroid figcaption { font-size: 0.7rem; text-align: center; margin-top: 6px; color: var(--color-muted); }
  .elsewhere { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .elsewhere li { margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
  .credits { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-muted); }
  .f1-tracks { margin: 2.5rem 0; padding: 1.5rem 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); }
  .track-label { font-size: 0.8rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; color: var(--color-muted); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .track-row { display: flex; gap: 2rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .track-item { text-align: center; cursor: default; }
  .track-item svg { width: 80px; height: 80px; color: var(--color-muted); transition: color 0.2s, transform 0.2s; }
  .track-item:hover svg { color: var(--color-accent); transform: scale(1.1); }
  .track-item span { display: block; font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-muted); margin-top: 4px; }
  .sticker { position: fixed; font-size: 1.6rem; opacity: 0.12; pointer-events: none; user-select: none; z-index: -1; }
  .s-michigan { top: 12%; right: 4%; transform: rotate(-8deg); font-size: 2rem; }
  .s-f1 { top: 28%; right: 6%; transform: rotate(12deg); }
  .s-aws { top: 45%; right: 3%; transform: rotate(-5deg); }
  .s-wine { top: 60%; right: 7%; transform: rotate(15deg); }
  .s-ski { top: 18%; left: 3%; transform: rotate(10deg); }
  .s-golf { top: 38%; left: 5%; transform: rotate(-12deg); }
  .s-france { top: 55%; left: 3%; transform: rotate(6deg); }
  .s-un { top: 72%; left: 5%; transform: rotate(-8deg); }
  @media (max-width: 1100px) { .sticker { display: none; } }
  @media (max-width: 500px) { .polaroid-grid { overflow-x: auto; } }
</style>
